extendedInfo.description: Attijari Mobile BankingCommercial Bank of Dubai   Keep your bank in the palm of your hand with Attijari Mobile Banking. Convenient, flexible and secure, With a completely personal and enhanced banking experience, using our new generation banking platform, at your fingertips this service is accessible anytime and anywhere with internet connection and through your mobile device. What can you do?YOU can â¦.    View account summary and transactions of your Current, Savings, Deposit, Loan accounts and Credit / Debit Cards    Make Utility Bill Payments to various companies like Etisalat, Du, DEWA, Salik etc    Find your nearest CBD ATM or Branch with Real time positioning using maps    Inquiry of products & services tailored for your benefits.    Transfer funds between your own accounts    Transfer funds to another CBD accounts    Transfer funds to accounts outside UAE (Remittances) Is it safe?Some of the security features:    Personalized activation/registration process with unique one time activation code    Secure registration process through Attijari Online banking    Multilevel checks using personal password/pin or using security token    Control your beneficiaries by adding or Removing utilities bills, internal and external payments details by Synchronization from Attijari Online Banking
